<p>El Capitan (?finally) provides a mechanism called Split View to Have two apps side-by-side in full screen mode.</p>  <p>I want to know if there exists, or how I'd go about implementing, a keyboard shortcut to switch/swap the panes while in Split View.</p>  <p>That is to say that the intended behaviour trigger is to take the left-pane and make it the right-pane and take the right-pane and make it the left-pane.</p>